stylometry:
Sensitivity analysis can be performed on an already existing problem.  It is the act of altering the changing cells in order to find the optimal solution.  Sensitivity analysis then provides a table that shows the results with different quantities for the changing cells.  

It is important because it provides the company and management a fuller, better, understanding of the problem and model.  As well as helps to make the best business like decision because the company can compare the opportunity costs while looking at the table.  They can see at what point the company will make money, and at what point the company would be losing money.
